{
  "text": "Biogenic silica contains loosely-bound oxygen (i.e. H 2 O, OHgroups) reaching up to 7e12% by weight [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] ) that needs to be removed prior to isotope analysis. Before d",
